{"tid":337603,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[報答養育之恩] 做整野食孝順老母 有咩推介？","createTime":"2017-07-27T12:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T15:46:35.000Z","uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e71a404b455d236d2128361a665c26126a9b3396","tid":337603,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"出世到呢家都未整過野比呀媽食 呢家最後一年暑假 再唔整我驚日後會忙冇時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想問問有咩野食易整又好味 d老母又多數會鍾意食？無論係主食定甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望癲狗巴打睇到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nps 呀媽因為要醫病做緊電療 生冷野唔食得"},{"pid":"12bd57011e5b81253044a7ac267e14b1967f0c76","tid":337603,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5d83d986bac3167320f5c38a01233828c16e09","tid":337603,"uid":79735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"認真答你<br />\n白飯+菜心炒牛肉+煎蛋<br />\n唔好整得太難食就已經好好"},{"pid":"7d51403add0baf4ca6efa6c51fcae9f12bab7173","tid":337603,"uid":113610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:33:31.000Z","msg":"其實 煲粥 都好足夠<br />\n心意黎"},{"pid":"35eff791cfdb635e1e8e61c9c88a43fa98e37019","tid":337603,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實 煲粥 都好足夠<br />\n心意黎</blockquote><br />\n佢唔係病到訓係床果d 佢仲係可以日日落街買送煲劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都多謝巴打既建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579ef6c4cc724f1c77509c2602faf8dcb1bbdb0e","tid":337603,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真答你<br />\n白飯+菜心炒牛肉+煎蛋<br />\n唔好整得太難食就已經好好</blockquote><br />\n即係正正常常家常便飯咁？"},{"pid":"cfb99f2d034ec54541481c6bd391b67ac3977fd4","tid":337603,"uid":19858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"視乎樓主阿媽鐘意食清淡定咩<br />\n不過通常老母都好踏實、賢淑<br />\n人到中年甚至晚年人生百味已嚐盡<br />\n反而追求反璞歸真<br />\n我媽媽最鐘意食就係蒸魚+雞+普通不過既炒菜<br />\n非常簡單<br />\n<br />\n糖水有好有壞<br />\n有D上年紀既會惹痰<br />\n一係就煲湯囉<br />\n大家都有得滋潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99adea0ce962c35510a0210034c9bc1ccf0e0c5","tid":337603,"uid":19858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"btw祝你媽媽身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可以10點半睇下鼎爺拎下靈感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢有D餸都幾油膩同複雜"},{"pid":"da0bcd70872a20c90afbdf7925a922dca6ecd738","tid":337603,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>視乎樓主阿媽鐘意食清淡定咩<br />\n不過通常老母都好踏實、賢淑<br />\n人到中年甚至晚年人生百味已嚐盡<br />\n反而追求反璞歸真<br />\n我媽媽最鐘意食就係蒸魚+雞+普通不過既炒菜<br />\n非常簡單<br />\n<br />\n糖水有好有壞<br />\n有D上年紀既會惹痰<br />\n一係就煲湯囉<br />\n大家都有得滋潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n煲湯我諗佢勁我好多倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但補既湯唔係多數都唔好飲？"},{"pid":"a1eb22f97edcc8b53bab1f32fc30491e0e073231","tid":337603,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw祝你媽媽身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可以10點半睇下鼎爺拎下靈感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢有D餸都幾油膩同複雜</blockquote><br />\n佢又係女人病 好彩發現得早 做下電療就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇睇電視好耐 搵日煲下mytv先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c22fa9453cb7b860a54e8134245eb1d855b8e9e","tid":337603,"uid":